{"tid":38972,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"以為增強免疫力！女子喝粥加兩顆「紅豆」　差點被毒死","createTime":"2016-12-14T09:24:16.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-17T06:22:58.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"55ed85e86cd123c00e7bedf0966a630c5d549abb","tid":38972,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T09:24:16.000Z","msg":"以為增強免疫力！女子喝粥加兩顆「紅豆」　差點被毒死！ <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=206805\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D206805&d=nkbfWGSnA4Gd6TbsJLrb13vMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=772b56b9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D206805&h=5d17fb01\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=206805</a> <br />\n<br />\n2016/12/13 13:13:00 <br />\n<br />\n大陸中心／綜合報導 <br />\n<br />\n天氣慢慢轉涼，許多人都喜歡來碗紅豆湯養氣補血，但並不是所有的「紅豆」都能吃的，大陸就有一名女子因為在煮粥時，加了兩顆這種豆子，結果差點連命都沒了。 <br />\n<br />\n據陸媒報導，大陸杭州一位20歲年輕女子，近日聽朋友說吃這種「紅豆」可以增強免疫力，於是在煮粥的時候放了兩顆，沒想到，吃完後覺得腹脹不適趕緊送醫急診，還差點丟了性命。醫師追蹤吃了什麼，一查竟是「相思豆」。 <br />\n<br />\n醫師表示，「相思豆」雖然長得像紅豆、綠豆，但其實是劇毒植物。由於「相思豆」顏色艷麗，很多人把它串成手鍊作為工藝品，曾經還有報導製作工人在串手鍊時，不慎穿破相思豆外殼，並扎破自己的手指後中毒身亡。 <br />\n<br />\n而民眾若是一旦誤食「相思豆」（嚼碎2-3粒），輕者噁心、嘔吐、腹瀉、腸絞痛等症狀，重者數日後可出現溶血、心跳乏力，甚至昏迷、呼吸、腎功能衰竭而死。 <br />\n<br />\n醫師提醒，許多人在冬天會選擇中藥進補食療，切勿服用一些不知名的植物、中藥、食物或藥酒。如果忽視了它們的毒性，很可能沒有起到應有治療效果，反而因此而中毒。若是不幸誤服，需即刻到醫院就診，以免錯過最佳治療時間。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://attach.azureedge.net/newsimages/2016/12/13/741991-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fattach.azureedge.net%2Fnewsimages%2F2016%2F12%2F13%2F741991-XXL.jpg&h=d97af9f5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"18f28e8ed7d6bf130a8961c298c1cb08420f187a","tid":38972,"uid":54344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T09:24:57.000Z","msg":"樋屋奇應丸？"},{"pid":"f77add14180d531b58d7f3e0c6be6b6c779cd794","tid":38972,"uid":55695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T09:29:13.000Z","msg":"睇過紅豆篇野？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc58022a705b5c12916ba0e8816467aeea6fc5a3","tid":38972,"uid":59684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T09:30:49.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"c58b0d8bec90b30c384d9527079ee8821c502d7b","tid":38972,"uid":35946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T09:42:57.000Z","msg":"除左有忽紅色之外，似紅豆咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89f02ff5109106f15e683f661fc26ef94e6e8d46","tid":38972,"uid":51932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T09:46:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>除左有忽紅色之外，似紅豆咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大陸呀，唔好深究啦"},{"pid":"50877c41fe088152e13af58d7548042be5f72666","tid":38972,"uid":39733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T09:57:58.000Z","msg":"邊度搵得到呢種豆？"},{"pid":"a9cd04a64f2a5de49b4c4e8ab792bd864422e835","tid":38972,"uid":683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T10:03:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>除左有忽紅色之外，似紅豆咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大陸呀，唔好深究啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢粒野本名真係叫紅豆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n王維既《相思》「紅豆生南國，春來發幾枝。願君多採擷，此物最相思。」就係講緊呢隻豆，係王維作左呢首詩之後，d人先叫呢隻豆做「相思豆」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1fe2e2e893b65cf052ded6768b3b16cb42b666b","tid":38972,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T05:30:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0589cc8a79c75f1cde086f4ad95a5798b8dc4189","tid":38972,"uid":34036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T05:39:24.000Z","msg":"咁都睇錯就抵死啦"},{"pid":"c3c144c6ebe2f08d3ca16d83bc711759cf0b5399","tid":38972,"uid":54673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T06:22:58.000Z","msg":"絕情花   斷腸草"}]}